BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Material and Light: A Conversation with Artist Nancy Lorenz
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260328T140000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260328T150000
UID:10001957-1774706400-1774710000@www.taubmanmuseum.org
DESCRIPTION:Nancy Lorenz: The Elements			\n		\n	\n\n\n\n\n\n	\n		\n			\n		
 		\n									\n				\n				\n								\n					Nancy Lorenz\, Moonlight\, 2023\
 , silver leaf\, mother of pearl\, shellac\, pigment on wood panel\, 36 x 6
 0 in.\, courtesy of the artist				\n							\n		\n	\n\n\n\n	\n		\n			\n\n	\
 n		\n\nGet an extra special sneak peek at an upcoming exhibition with arti
 st Nancy Lorenz in advance of her solo exhibition\, The Elements\, openi
 ng February 2027 here at the Taubman Museum of Art. \n\n\n\nIn conversatio
 n with Curator Laura K. Higgins\, Lorenz will explore her distinctive pr
 actice\, which draws on a lifetime of engagement with rich materials and s
 urface techniques.  \n\n\n\nLorenz’s luminous works—layered with gold
 \, silver\, and palladium leaf\, mother-of-pearl inlay\, resin\, and lacqu
 er—reflect both Western abstraction and deep influence from traditional 
 Japanese craft and aesthetics\, a sensibility first seeded during her form
 ative years in Tokyo. \n\n\n\nPresented in dialogue with selections of Jap
 anese prints and a kimono from the Museum’s Sharing Collection\, this pr
 ogram situates Lorenz’s material language within broader artistic and c
 ultural lineages\, offering insight into the ideas and influences that wil
 l shape her forthcoming exhibition. \n\n\n\nMembers Free | General Public:
  $8 \n\n\n\nNot a Member? Join today and receive benefits such as discount
 s on classes and camps\, invitations to exclusive events\, free reciprocal
  membership to the Virginia Museum of Fine Arts in Richmond\, and more! Cl
 ick here to learn more.  \n\n	\n\n\n\n	\n				\n			\n				\n			\n			\n				Ad
 d to Calendar\n								\n			\n		\n				\n			\n				\n					\n				\n			\n			\n
 				Driving? Get Directions\n			\n		\n		\n			\n				\n			\n			\n				Share  
 This!\n			\n		\n						\n			\n				\n			\n			\n				Register Now\n			\n		\n		
 	\n	\n				\n		\n						\n				\n					\n						Date:					 \n					\n						\n			
 				\n								\n									Feb 04\, 2027								\n								\n																
 											\n											May 16\, 2027\n\nSource: https://www.taubmanmuseum
 .org/conversation-with-nancy-lorenz
LOCATION:Taubman Museum of Art\, 110 Salem Ave SE\, Roanoke\, VA\, 24011\,
  United States
URL:https://www.taubmanmuseum.org/conversation-with-nancy-lorenz
X-SOURCE:Taubman Museum of Art
